Subject:[MG] [INVITATION] 2012-11-05 - fundiert-entscheiden.de -
	International E-Democracy Talk IV
Hi Folks!

The working group 'AG Meinungsfindungstool' of the Pirate Party Germany 
would like to invite you to the 4th International E-Democracy Talk!


WHEN?

Monday, 5th November 2012
Start 9.30pm UTC+1

>> Please be aware that we are back on winter time now <<


WHAT?

Karsten Weihe presents the concept and idea behind the internet portal 
"fundiert-entscheiden.de".

  fundiert entscheiden = decide on a sound basis
  A collaborative plattform for systematic, factual, to-the-point edition of 
controversial questions of all kinds.

Please read the following pdf for more detailed information (german only):
http://dl.dropbox.com/u/52844031/Einf%C3%BChrung%20in%20fundiert-entscheiden.de.pdf

For an english version of the conceptual overview please click below:
http://dl.dropbox.com/u/52844031/Poster%20English%20fundiert-entscheiden.de.pdf


WHERE?

Server: mumble.piratenpartei-nrw.de
Port: 64738 (standard)
User: <any>
Passwort: <none>
Raum: Bund / Arbeitsgemeinschaften / Technik(IT) / AG Meinungsfindungstool

You don't know Mumble? Click on the link below to learn more:
http://mumble.sourceforge.net/


WHY?

Choose one of the following:

A) Share knowledge to learn from each other.
B) Join forces to upgrade democracy.
C) Prepare for the future.



